UrBackup server has been installed!

You have to follow this steps to configure UrBackup for the first time
1) Stop the jail
2) Map the folders:
2a) /mnt/backups/urbackup   (inside the jail) to the dataset outside the jail where you want to store your backups
2b) /var/urbackup           (inside the jail) to the dataset outside the jail where you want to store the UrBackup database files
2c) /usr/local/etc/urbackup (inside the jail) to the dataset outside the jail where you want to store the UrBackup configuration files
3) Start the jail
4) Browse to http://jail-ip:55414 and configure an admin user.

Official homepage is https://www.urbackup.org/index.html
